        </h2>

        {/* FAQ Accordion */}
        <div className="space-y-4">
          {[
            {
              q: "HOW DOES THE AI COMIC GENERATOR WORK?",
              a: "Our AI analyzes your story input and selected style (Comic, Manga, or Manhwa) to generate unique, high-quality comic panels. You can write your own story or use our 'Inspire Me' feature to get AI-generated plot ideas. The AI then creates artwork that matches your chosen universe (Star Wars, Disney, Naruto, DBZ, or Harry Potter) while making you the hero of the story."
            },
            {
              q: "CAN I REALLY BE THE HERO IN MY OWN COMIC?",
              a: "Absolutely! That's the core feature of our platform. You become the main character in your personalized comic book. Whether you want to be a Jedi in Star Wars, a wizard in Harry Potter, or a Saiyan in DBZ, our AI creates a story where you're the protagonist."
            },
            {
              q: "WHAT STYLES ARE AVAILABLE?",
              a: "We offer three distinct artistic styles: Comic (Western superhero style), Manga (Japanese anime style), and Manhwa (Korean webtoon style). Each style has its own unique visual characteristics and storytelling approach."
            },
            {
              q: "WHICH UNIVERSES CAN I CHOOSE FROM?",
              a: "Currently, we support five popular universes: Star Wars, Disney, Naruto, Dragon Ball Z, and Harry Potter. Each universe comes with its own themed fonts, color schemes, and storytelling elements to create an authentic experience."
            },
            {
              q: "DO I NEED TO WRITE MY OWN STORY?",
              a: "No! While you can write your own story for complete creative control, we also offer an 'Inspire Me' button that generates compelling story ideas for you. You can use these AI-generated plots as-is or modify them to fit your vision."
            },
            {
              q: "HOW LONG DOES IT TAKE TO CREATE A COMIC?",
              a: "The generation process typically takes just a few minutes, depending on the length and complexity of your story. Once you submit your story and preferences, our AI works quickly to create your personalized comic."
            },
            {
              q: "CAN I ORDER A PHYSICAL BOOK?",
              a: "Yes! We provide high-resolution digital comics that are perfect for printing. You can order a physical book version of your comic, which makes an amazing gift or personal keepsake. The printing service is optional and available after you create your comic."
            },
            {
              q: "WHAT RESOLUTION ARE THE COMICS?",
              a: "All comics are generated in high resolution, suitable for both digital viewing and professional printing. The output quality ensures crisp, clear images whether you're reading on screen or holding a physical book."
            },
            {
              q: "CAN I EDIT MY COMIC AFTER IT'S GENERATED?",
              a: "Yes! You can regenerate your comic with different settings, modify your story, or try different artistic styles and universes. You have full control to iterate until you're completely satisfied with the result."
            },
            {
              q: "IS THERE A LIMIT TO HOW MANY COMICS I CAN CREATE?",
              a: "This depends on your subscription plan. Our Starter plan includes 1 course, Pro offers unlimited courses, and Academy provides unlimited everything. Check our pricing section for detailed plan comparisons."
            },
            {
              q: "CAN I USE THIS FOR EDUCATIONAL PURPOSES?",
              a: "Absolutely! Many teachers use our platform to create educational comics for their students. It's a fantastic way to make learning engaging by turning students into characters in historical events, scientific discoveries, or literary adventures."
            },
            {
              q: "CAN I CREATE COMICS AS GIFTS?",
              a: "Yes! Our comics make incredibly unique and personal gifts. Many users create custom comics for birthdays, anniversaries, graduations, or other special occasions. The physical book option makes it even more special."
            },
            {
              q: "DO I OWN THE RIGHTS TO MY CREATED COMICS?",
              a: "You retain full ownership of the stories you write and the comics generated from them. However, please note that universes like Star Wars, Disney, etc., are trademarked properties, so commercial use may be restricted."
            },
            {
              q: "CAN I SHARE MY COMICS ON SOCIAL MEDIA?",
              a: "Yes! You're free to share your digital comics on social media platforms. Many users love sharing their creations with friends and family online."
            },
            {
              q: "WHAT IF I'M NOT SATISFIED WITH THE RESULT?",
              a: "You can regenerate your comic as many times as you need with different settings or story modifications. Our AI learns from your preferences to deliver better results with each iteration."
            },
            {
              q: "IS MY STORY DATA KEPT PRIVATE?",
              a: "Yes, we take privacy seriously. Your stories and personal data are kept confidential and secure. We never share your creative content with third parties."
            },
            {
              q: "CAN I COLLABORATE WITH OTHERS?",
              a: "Our Academy plan includes team accounts, allowing multiple users to collaborate on projects. This is perfect for schools, creative teams, or families working together."
            },
            {
              q: "DO YOU OFFER REFUNDS?",
              a: "We offer a satisfaction guarantee. If you're not happy with our service, please contact our support team within the first 30 days for a full refund."
            },
            {
              q: "WHAT PAYMENT METHODS DO YOU ACCEPT?",
              a: "We accept all major credit cards, PayPal, and other popular payment methods. All transactions are secured and encrypted for your safety."
            },
            {
              q: "HOW DO I GET STARTED?",
              a: "Simply click the 'Get Started' or 'Start for free' button, choose your style and universe, write or generate your story, and let our AI create your personalized comic! The process is intuitive and takes just minutes."
            }
          ].map((faq, index) => (
            <div key={index} className="bg-white border-[3px] border-black shadow-[4px_4px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)]">
              <button
                onClick={() => {
                  const answer = document.getElementById(`faq-${index}`);
                  const icon = document.getElementById(`icon-${index}`);
                  if (answer && icon) {
                    answer.classList.toggle('hidden');
                    icon.classList.toggle('rotate-90');
                  }
                }}
                className="w-full px-6 py-4 flex items-center justify-between text-left hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors"
              >
                <span className="font-black text-sm md:text-base pr-4">{faq.q}</span>
                <div
                  id={`icon-${index}`}
                  className="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-[#facc15] border-[2px] border-black rounded-full flex items-center justify-center transition-transform duration-300"
                >
                  <ChevronRight className="w-5 h-5 text-black" strokeWidth={3} />
                </div>
              </button>
              <div id={`faq-${index}`} className="hidden px-6 pb-4">
                <p className="text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">{faq.a}</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
